quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  11,121,"Kí o sì sọ fún àwọn tí kò gbàgbọ́ pé: “Ẹ máa ṣe bí ẹ ti fẹ́ nínú ẹ̀sìn yín. Dájúdájú àwa náà yóò máa bá ẹ̀sìn wa lọ."
  11,122,"Ẹ máa retí, dájúdájú Àwa náà ń retí.”"
  11,123,"Ti Allāhu ni ìkọ̀kọ̀ àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ sì ni wọ́n máa ṣẹ́rí gbogbo ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá padà sí pátápátá. Nítorí náà, jọ́sìn fún Un, kí o sì gbáralé E. Olúwa rẹ kì í sì ṣe onígbàgbéra nípa n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  12,82,"Kí o sì bi àwọn ará ìlú tí a wà nínú rẹ̀ àti èrò-ràkúnmí tí a jọ darí dé léèrè wò. Dájúdájú olódodo ni wá.”"
  12,83,"(Ànábì Ya‘ƙūb) sọ pé: “Rárá o, ẹ̀mí yín ló ṣe ọ̀ràn kan lọ́ṣọ̀ọ́ fún yín. Nítorí náà, sùúrù tó rẹwà (lọ̀rọ̀ mi kàn báyìí). Ó ṣeé ṣe kí Allāhu bá mi mú gbogbo wọn wá. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Onímọ̀, Ọlọ́gbọ́n.”"
  12,84,"Ó pa wọ́n tì, ó sì sọ pé: “Ìbànújẹ́ ń bẹ fún mi lórí Yūsuf!” Ojú rẹ̀ méjèèjì sì funfun wá (kò ríran mọ́) látara ìbànújẹ́ náà; ó sì pa á mọ́ra."
  14,28,"Ṣé o kò wòye sí àwọn tó yí ìdẹ̀ra Allāhu padà sí àìgbàgbọ́, wọ́n sì mú ìjọ wọn gúnlẹ̀ sí ilé ìparun?"
  14,29,"Iná Jahanamọ ni wọn yóò gúnlẹ̀ sí; ibùgbé náà sì burú."
  14,30,"Wọ́n sọ (àwọn kan di) akẹgbẹ́ fún Allāhu nítorí kí wọ́n lè ṣẹ́rí àwọn ènìyàn kúrò nínú ẹ̀sìn Rẹ̀. Sọ pé: “Ẹ máa gbádùn ǹsó, nítorí pé dájúdájú inú Iná ni ẹ máa gúnlẹ̀ sí.”"
  15,1,"’Alif lām rọ̄. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)Ìwọ̀nyí ni àwọn āyah Tírà náà àti (àwọn āyah) al-Ƙur’ān tó ń yanjú ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá. {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  15,2,"Ó ṣeé ṣe kí àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nífẹ̀ẹ́ sí pé àwọn ìbá sì ti jẹ́ mùsùlùmí (nílé ayé)."
  15,3,"Fi wọ́n sílẹ̀, kí wọ́n jẹ, kí wọ́n gbádùn, kí ìrètí (ẹ̀mí gígùn) kó àìrójú ráàyè bá wọn (láti ṣẹ̀sìn); láìpẹ́ wọ́n máa mọ̀."